    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per the ASME V&V 40 requirements matrix. Validation results demonstrate that CFD predictions of hemolysis index are within acceptable error bounds across the COU operating envelope. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1.0 criterion is satisfied at all 5 operating points. The model is accepted as fit for purpose to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
